import Page from './main'

function App() {
    return (
    <>
        <Page 
        img = '/assets/img1.png'
        name = 'Japan 🎌'
        />
        <Page
        img = '/assets/img2.png'
        name = 'America 🌠'
        />
        <Page 
        img = '../assets/img3.png'
        name = 'fantacy 🌏'
        />
    </>
        
    )
}

export default App
